# RfEmpImp

## Random-forest-based Multiple Imputation using Empirical Out-of-bag Prediction Error Distribtuion 

Example:
```r
library(RfEmpImp)
impObj <- mice(nhanes, method = "rfempimp", m = 10, max.iter = 10)

```
